snippet.title: Inside the Arena: Vehicles & Weapons
snippet.description:
Our team gives you a behind-the-scenes look at the new vehicles and weapons in PlanetSide Arena, launching January 29, 2019.
Learn more and pre-order now: https://www.planetsidearena.com
